157.title: Cancun Vacation 2018
157.plot: Come along with the Iseli family as they head back to Cancun Mexico for the second year in a row for their family vacation.

158.title: Cancun Vacation 2018 Part 2
158.plot: Come along with the Iseli family as they continue their Cancun vacation by visiting Xcaret. Xcaret is an amazing theme park in Mexico with so much to do it would take more than just one day to do it all, but they tried.

159.title: Cancun Vacation 2018 Part 3
159.plot: The Iselis wrap up their Cancun vacation with some shopping and an amazing dinner at a four-star restaurant. The vacation was just perfect until they tried to leave and got stuck at the Dallas Fortworth airport for 28 hours.

160.title: New home and New Adventures
160.plot: Join Wes, Natalie, and Lana as they sign the papers for their new home. You will be right there for their first little touch to make it their very own. You will see how the shed company dropped the gym in the backyard, you will see Lana's new home-school area, Lana lose her first tooth, and even come along with family as they travel to do close up magic at a luncheon for a company party.

161.title: Round Hill Farm 2018
161.plot: Come along with the Iselis as they perform at Round Hill Farm again this year. They were hired to perform every Saturday and Sunday this October. With hayrides, pumpkin picking, moon bounces, hay mazes, a corn maze and much more this place has so much to do. Adding a magician to the mix was icing on the cake.

162.title: Halloween 2018
162.plot: Join the Iselis as they go picking apples at Carter Mountain. You will also get to see where they are on a few projects in their backyard like their gym, work shed, and animal barn. You will then go along with them as they travel to Roanoke to spend Halloween with Natalie's family so Lana can go trick or treating with her cousins.

163.title: Belfort Furniture Grand Opening
163.plot: The Iselis travel to Dulles, Virginia to perform at Belfort Furniture's Grand Opening. Wes worked this event over 3 days in 2 weekends. The craziest day was when they brought in The Property Brothers from HGTV to take photos with fans; while they were taking photos Wes performed on the red carpet.

164.title: 2018 Holiday Season Kickoff
164.plot: Travel to Bowie, Maryland with the Iselis and watch them perform at an elementary school. You will also see them perform at a church they visit each year. This video ends with a tour of their new animal shed which is almost complete and Lana also makes a special phone call with Santa.

165.title: Saying goodbye is hard to do
165.plot: Wes and Natalie go on their final walk-through of their old house. They give a full tour of the old house and share some precious memories.

166.title: Getting into the Christmas Spirit
166.plot: Join the family as they pick out the Iseli family Christmas tree. You will also come along as they attend a tree lighting ceremony in our new hometown and more.

167.title: Performing at the MGM Grand Hotel and Casino
167.plot: Hang out with the Iseli's on a show-free snow day, then come along as they perform at the MGM Grand in Maryland for the first time.

168.title: Lana Turns 7
168.plot: Celebrate Lana's birthday a few days early with a bunch of her friends. You will also get to come along with the Iseli's as they head over to a Fox television station to be interviewed about their charity work. Later that evening while performing at the Children's Hospital, Wes was interviewed again for the evening news. This video ends with Lana opening more presents on her real birthday.

169.title: New Years Eve 2018
169.plot: Hang out with Wes as he performs 6 straight hours of close up magic at Hyatt Regency Resort in Cambridge Maryland on New Years Eve. Lana and Natalie also got to partake in other activities that evening like the ball drop for kids and the moon bounce room. After midnight the family wrapped up the evening by opening a bottle of sparkling juice for Lana and champagne for themselves back in our hotel room.

170.title: A Lazy week in January
170.plot: Wes, Natalie, and Lana take it easy and enjoy the ice and snow that was dropped on them during the week. The end of this video shows Lana's most recent ballet recital.

171.title: Science Museum of Virginia
171.plot: The Iselis travel to Richmond and visit the Science Museum where they had a lot of fun playing, learning and exploring.

172.title: Kidvention 2019
172.plot: The Iselis head up to northern Virginia to go to an annual Magic Convention for Children's entertainers. Natalie and Wes don't attend this convention but enjoy going to the gala show for Lana and we get to see a bunch of friends as well.

imdb.plot outline: What is a Magic Life? For Wes Iseli, a Magic Life consists of well-timed opportunities and privileges with good old-fashioned hard work. There's no better example of successful living than that of the Magician and Illusionist from Ruckersville, Virginia, who faces his barrage of trials and tribulations just like you and I, but purposely turns them into advantages and opportunities. Wes wants everyone to stop seeking ways to be happy and start finding them, by watching what he does and applying his techniques to become their own success. There are tricks to living a Magic Life. Watch closely. This family man who performs over 400 shows a year holds nothing up his sleeves, but you won't want to miss a thing. See what happens on stage and off when you follow Wes Iseli's Magic Life in pursuit of your own.
